        "ccda2d60-ae14-4857-8a1c-e18338400ab0": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "paragraph": "<p></p><p>All of our reclaimed wood furniture is available in 4 colours. <br/><br/><strong>Warm </strong><em>- Our warm finish is a mid-brown natural wax with a hint of honey tones which creates a beautiful rich colour without being too dark. The perfect colour to give your home a warm and inviting feeling.</em></p><p><strong><br/>Grey </strong><em>- Our grey finish is a unique colour wash which is sealed with a natural clear wax. This creates calming tones and a contemporary finish without losing the natural rustic character.</em></p><p><strong><br/>Classic </strong><em>- Our classic finish is the darkest of our natural waxes. A classic brown colour with sumptous deep and rich tones that blend together to give a stunning timeless and luxurious finish.</em></p><p><strong><br/>Natural </strong><em>- Our natural finish uses a clear wax that brings out all the natural tones and colours in the wood, highlighting the genuine character of each beam.</em><br/></p><p>When you order a free set of our 4 wood colour samples, they'll arrive in a letterbox-friendly package. </p><p>For custom metal frame samples and fabric colour options <em>( Annabel dining chairs) </em>please call us on <a href=\"tel:01159700060\" title=\"tel:01159700060\">01159 700 060</a> to discuss options.</p>"
          }
        }
